  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00641:a949fbc8be10]]\nsample spec 的路径只能相对 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00642:cb89034958ab]]。每个样本必须声明：",
  "read_only_context_before": "这里不能把[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00623:b03c6980982f]]写成[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00624:8105ccaedd57]]。hash 只能证明版本身份，不能证明模型真正遵循了句长、标点、第一人称或收尾习惯。因此 v12 只把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00625:f221ebb6bfb3]] 从固定未评估升级成真实的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00626:d117c014ce6b]]；[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00627:eeb486c1293c]] 仍保持 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00628:b267cecfa13a]]。",
